Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.54,CN,,0,0,0,,小泉？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.98,0:03:11.21,CN,,0,0,0,,你是泉新一吧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.82,CN,,0,0,0,,那个…
